Hello fellow Nexus users!

This is my first mod that I have released so far. I have never made a mod in my life so if there are any problems, let me know. The mod adds in a new follower in Jorrvaskr which is a female Nord.
Please give back as much good feedback as possible it will really help
Have a great day playing Skyrim
MagicRene
